{"_path":"/construction/c36","_dir":"construction","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"長慶一街打通銜接文德路","description":null,"image":"/images/construction/c36-1.jpeg","sequence":36,"category":"工商發展","status":"3.規劃","type":null,"budget":null,"link":"https://www.facebook.com/TYleehao/posts/pfbid02gBiuV6CFcaMYFiMydReXbcPGwUYfEtENKWQcnqyetFWQS5AJ4xiE8e3XHrUcEnPKl","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2030-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"長慶一街打通銜接文德路"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長慶一街打通銜接文德路"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"計畫概要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫概要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 長慶一街打通銜接文德路"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"類別 交通建設 - CON-36"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完工 待定？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費 1 億 6 千萬"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"狀態 完成都市計劃變更"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2024/11/14:\n求長慶一街打通 ❗️"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n這條道路是連接長庚里、樂善里和 A7 重劃區的關鍵瓶頸道路，雅倫於 110 年就要求評估打通。\n目前長慶一街已完成都市計畫變更，隨著重劃區人口成長，打通需求愈發急迫。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n因此這次我也當面跟市長建議，無論市府是要跟長庚合作開發，或是利用林口都市計畫內的都市發展基金專款專用，支付約 1 億 4500 萬元的用地費，僅需再編列 1500 萬元的工程費便可加速開闢長慶一街！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n圖片為桃園市都發局長，我也現場跟局長確認經費來源沒有問題，希望市府加速進行，讓地方交通更順暢！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c36-2.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c36-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在樂田田社區前打通長慶一街通往文德路的銜接。讓長庚醫護社區往長庚校區車輛能直接進入長慶一街 減少長慶三街車流。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/pamg4jkeLJCHaFVp/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2024/11/05:\n110 年最早提案推動【長慶一街至長庚路】已完成都市計畫變更"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/TYleehao/posts/pfbid02gBiuV6CFcaMYFiMydReXbcPGwUYfEtENKWQcnqyetFWQS5AJ4xiE8e3XHrUcEnPKl"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2024/07/03 宗豪也在議會持續追蹤「長慶一街瓶頸道路打通」，要求加速進度，串連長慶一二三街生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"建設詳情"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建設詳情"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c36-1.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c36-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"長慶一街打通銜接文德路","depth":2,"text":"長慶一街打通銜接文德路","children":[{"id":"計畫概要","depth":3,"text":"計畫概要"},{"id":"建設詳情","depth":3,"text":"建設詳情"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:construction:c36.md","_source":"content","_file":"construction/c36.md","_extension":"md"}